  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Expert dialogue on development (engagement of partners in development cooperation)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Academics, university students, policy makers, members of parliament, media</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project  in a long-term perspective aims at forming a group of Slovak experts conversant with the issues facing developing countries and engaged in development cooperation activities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022;	To increase awareness of target groups about the relevant issued facing developing countries, about development assistance provided by the Slovak Republic.
&#x2022;	To increase the participation of target groups in the field of development cooperation. 

In order to achieve these goals, various activities are implied for students (educational courses and practical trainings as well as incentives for writing academic papers) and academics (promotion of discussion among them, oppotunity to gain experience abroad, etc.)</narrative>
  </description>
